criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  IPSS>20;

          -  maximum urinary flow rate< 10ml\s (Qmax);

          -  ineffective alfa-blockers therapy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  histologically verified prostate cancer;

          -  history of prostatic surgery;

          -  urethral strictures;

          -  bladder stones;

          -  chronic urinary retention and cystostomy.
